item.title: A starter blog
item.description: I have been reading a lot more after I left my previous job at NortonLifeLock as an SRE. It is nice to catch up with all the technology and tools that I was not using before. The day has only so many hours and at some point I was just burned out and too tired to keep going. Moreover, I still felt like after all these years I have not been sharing much of my thoughts and experiences with anyone other than close friends and family.
